  JOHANNESBURG - SARS Commissioner Edward Kieswetter says the finance minister has done a good job by addressing additional demands, like the investment in Eskom. Godongwana announced R254bn in debt relief for the power utility. Budget 2023 | Govt to provide Eskom R254bn in debt relief He says the relief will help improve Eskom's financial struggles but warned that the arrangement will be accompanied by strict conditions to safeguard public funds. Finance Minister Enoch Godongwana delivered the 2023 Budget Speech on Wednesday.